<div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-item">
        <label>Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" value="<%= author.name %>">
    </div>
</div>

<!--
'name' attribute in form tag is used by the server to fetch the object that is passed from the route.
whatever we type in the form field will be send back to server from the 'value' attribute.
-->